quran[9{c,v,t}:
3,92,"tum neki ko nahi poanch satke jab taq ke apni woh cheeze ( khuda ki raah mein ) kharch nah karo jinhein tum Aziz rakhtay ho, aur jo kuch tum kharch karo ge Allah is se be khabar nah hoga"
3,93,"khanay ki yeh saari cheeze ( jo Shariat Muhammad iSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam mein halal hain ) bani Israel ke liye bhi halal theen, Albata baaz cheeze aisi theen jinhein Touraat ke nazil kiye jaane se pehlay Israel ne khud apne oopar haraam kar liya tha un se kaho, agar tum ( a pannay aitraaz mein ) sachey ho to lao Touraat aur paish karo is ki koi ibaarat"
3,94,is ke baad bhjo log apni jhooti gharri hui baatein Allah ki taraf mansoob karte rahen o hi Dur haqeeqat zalim hain
3,95,"kaho, Allah ne jo kuch farmaya hai sach farmaya hai, tum ko yaksu ho kar ibrahim ke tareeqa ki pairwi karni chahiye, aur ibrahim shirk karne walon mein se nah tha"
3,96,be shak sab se pehli ibadat gaah jo insanon ke liye taamer hui woh wohi hai jo mecca mein waqay hai is ko kher o barket di gayi thi aur tamam Jahan walon ke liye markaz hadaayat banaya gaya tha
3,97,"is mein khuli hui nishanain hain, ibrahim ka maqam ibadat hai, aur iss ka haal yeh hai ke jo iss mein daakhil howa Mamoon ho gaya logon par Allah ka yeh haq hai ke jo is ghar taq pounchanay ki istetat rakhta ho woh is ka hajj kere, aur jo koi is hukum ki pairwi se inkaar kere to usay maloom ho jana chahiye ke Allah tamam daal naya walon se be niaz hai"
3,98,"kaho, ae ahal kitaab! tum kyun Allah ki baatein maan-ne se inkaar karte ho? jo harkatein tum kar rahay ho Allah sab kuch dekh raha hai"
3,99,"kaho, ae ahal kitaab! yeh tumhari kya rawish hai ke jo Allah ki baat maanta hai ussay bhi tum Allah ke rasta se roktay ho aur chahtay ho ke woh tedhi raah chalay, halaank tum khud ( is ke raah raast honay par ) gawah ho tumhari harkato se Allah ghaafil nahi hai"
3,100,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum ne inn ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh ki baat maani to yeh tumhe imaan se phir kufar ki taraf phair le jayen ge"
